ut it, custom entity models won't appear. For the best experience, it's recommended to use [OptiFine](https://optifine.net/downloads) or [Entity Model Features](https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features).\n\n<details>\n<summary>Notice</summary>\n  Custom Entity Models are a work in progress. Some entities may not yet have their custom models.\n</details>\n\n---\n\nThis resource pack is a port of the Egyptian Mythology Mash-up from Legacy Console Edition with updated textures from Bedrock Edition. Original textures by 4J Studios.\n</center>",
